'''地景流行病學'''是研究[[疾病|疾病]]與環境因素之間的關係的科學。類似[[地景生態學|地景生態學]]，<ref>Kitron, U. "Landscape Ecology and Epidemiology of Vector-Borne Diseases: Tools for Spatial Analysis." ''Journal of Medical Entomology.'' 1998(35):435-445.</ref>  地景流行病學經由分析風險模型和環境風險因素，來控制疾病的傳播。<ref>Pavlovsky, E.N. ''Natural Nidality of Transmissible Diseases, With Special Reference to the Landscape Epidemiology of Zooanthroponse.'' Urbana, Ill.: University of Illinois Press, 1966.</ref>

==歷史==
1996年，[[葉甫根尼·帕夫洛夫斯基|葉甫根尼·帕夫洛夫斯基]]提出了微觀上的病原體由環境系統整體決定的理論。<ref>Galuzo, I.G. "Landscape Epidemiology (epizootiology)." ''Advances in Veterinary Science & Comparative Medicine.'' 1975(19):73-96.</ref> 隨著[[地理信息系統|地理信息系統]]和[[遙感|遙感]]等技術的發展，以及地景生態學的完善，地景流行病學已經可以應用在研究許多疾病（例如[[瘧疾|瘧疾]]、[[漢他病毒|漢他病毒]]、[[萊姆病|萊姆病]]和[[恰加斯氏病|恰加斯氏病]]）上。<ref>Brownstein, J.S.; Rosen, H.; Purdy, D.; Miller, J.; Merlino, M.; Mostashari, F.; Fish, D. "Spatial Analysis of West Nile Virus: Rapid Risk Assessment of an Introduced Vector-Borne Zoonosis." ''Vector Borne and Zoonotic Diseases.'' 2(3):157-164.</ref>

